# Agent Autonomy

When working on this project, the agent may:

- **Run terminal commands** — Execute any needed commands (build, test, lint, scripts)
- **Install tools/dependencies** — npm, pip, Godot addons, system packages, etc.
- **Download resources** — Fetch packages, assets, docs, or other files when required

Do not ask for permission first. If a task needs a command, install, or download, just do it.
